<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
<div class="cover">
<div class="row" style="background-color: white; padding-bottom: 10px;">
  <h3 class="aboutHeader" style = "text-align: center; font-size: 30px;">During COVID-19<br>
    Can't socialize in person?<br>
    Drop in for fellowship on ThinQ.tv! 
  </h3>
</div>
<div class="row"style=" height: 500px; background-color:white; padding-top: 50px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.5);  padding-bottom: 100px; ">

  <div class="col-lg-6" style=" padding-left: 0px; padding-right:0px; ">
      <%= image_tag("connect.jpg", :class=>"img-responsive" , :style => "height:400px; width:120%;")%>
  </div>

  <div class="col-lg-6" style="background-color: white;height: 400px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.5);">
       <p style=" font-size:19px;  line-height: 2.5em;  padding-top: 60px;">

      - Invite friends & family to conversations when you'll be there so you can participate together. <br>
      - Invite seniors who are quarantined by sending them this link <%= link_to "http://www.ThinQ.tv/seniorliving", seniorliving_path%>
        OR email them directly 
        <button style="background-color: #8C1D40; border-radius: 4px; padding-top: 4px"><a href="mailto:?&subject=Join%20me%20at%20ThinQ.tv!&body=Every%20afternoon%20and%20evening%20ThinQ.tv%20has%20meaningful%20live%20video%20conversations%20to%20keep%20you%20from%20feeling%20isolated%20during%20COVID-19.%20A%20Fellowship%20Host%20will%20be%20live%20on%20ThinQ.tv%20to%20listen,%20play%20a%20trivia%20game,%20or%20even%20pray%20with%20you.%20Go%20to%20http://www.ThinQ.tv/seniorliving%20and%20click%20on%20Click%20Here%20to%20Join%20Fellowship%20Conversation." alt="Email" target="_blank" style="color: white">E-Mail &#9993</a></button> <br>
      - Spread the word about <span style="font-weight: bold; ">THINQ.TV </span> via 
        </p>
               <div class="col-sm-2">
               
                <% domainurl = "http://www.ThinQ.tv" %>
                <% desc = "Participate in thought-provoking conversations!"%>
              
                <!-- Share -->
                <script async defer crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v3.3"></script>
                <div class="social-share-button" data-href="<%= domainurl %>">
                  <!-- Facebook Share -->
                  <a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinq.tv%2F&amp;src=sdkpreparse"
                    onclick="window.open('https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinq.tv%2F&amp;src=sdkpreparse',
                    'newwindow',
                    'width=600,height=400,top=100,left=300');
                    return false;">
                    <img src="<%= asset_url('social-share-button/facebook.png') %>"></img>
                  </a>
                  <!-- Twitter Tweet -->
                  <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?hashtags=ThinQTV&text=Participate%20in%20live%20thought-provoking%20conversations%20or%20Host%20your%20own%20Live%20Video%20office%20hours!&tw_p=tweetbutton&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ThinQ.tv%2F"><img src="<%= asset_url('social-share-button/twitter.png') %>"></img></a>
                  <!-- LinkedIn Share -->
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=<%= domainurl %>&title=ThinQTV&summary=<%= desc %>" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'mywin',); return false;"><img src="<%= asset_url('social-share-button/linkedin.png') %>"/></a>
                  <!-- Email Share -->
                  <a href="mailto:?subject=Check out ThinQ.TV! Conversations to Make you ThinQ&amp;body=You are invited to check out <%= domainurl %>!%0D%0A%0D%0A<%= desc %>%0D%0A%0D%0AHost your own Live Video office hours on thought-provoking topics!%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A"><img src="<%= asset_url('social-share-button/email.png') %>"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3 pull-right" id="fb">

            </div>
 
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row" style="background-color: white; padding-top: 50px; padding-left: 200px; padding-bottom: 100px; ">

    <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="flip-card-container">
      <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-front">
          <%= image_tag("marker.jpg")%>
          <h3 style = " padding-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color:white"> What is THINQ.TV? </h3>
        </div>
      <div class="flip-card-back">
          <p>
            - ThinQ.tv is a platform where people can host live video fellowship online. <br><br> 
            - ThinQ.tv breaks the paradigm of “talking at” the internet, where one camera broadcasts live video at a social media platform and expects others to passively observe with little interaction.<br><br> 
            - Instead, ThinQ.tv is for “listening to” people. Everyone is welcome to participate in ThinQ.tv fellowship hours. <br><br>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="flip-card-container">
      <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-front">
          <%= image_tag("activities.jpg")%>
          <h3 style = " padding-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color:white">What You might want to talk about: </h3>
        </div>
      <div class="flip-card-back">
          <p>
           - News <br><br>
           - Books <br><br>
           - Trivia games <br><br>
           - You can even pray with others on THINQ.TV!. <br><br>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="flip-card-container">
      <div class="flip-card">
        <div class="flip-card-front">
          <%= image_tag("question.jpg")%>
          <h3 style = "padding-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color:white">Questions? </h3>
        </div>
      <div class="flip-card-back">
          <p>
            - Drop in to any of the live video YourOnlineMom conversations by Dr. Lisa Schaefer listed on the <%= link_to 'ThinQ.tv schedule', root_path %> so we can meet you. <br><br>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

